World Development Indicators data
=================================

The manydist package includes wdi_2022, a transformed subset of the World
Bank's World Development Indicators for reference year 2022. The snapshot was
retrieved on 2026-05-05 using the World Bank Indicators API.

Attribution: The World Bank: World Development Indicators.

The World Development Indicators dataset is licensed under the Creative
Commons Attribution 4.0 International license, subject to the World Bank
Dataset Terms and any conditions identified in the indicator metadata:

https://datacatalog.worldbank.org/search/dataset/0037712/world-development-indicators
https://www.worldbank.org/ext/en/legal/terms-conditions/datasets

The transformations applied by the manydist authors are documented in the
wdi_2022 help topic and in data-raw/wdi_2022.R in the package source
repository. Inclusion of these data does not imply endorsement by the World
Bank.
